review_blob: This is an Awesome Beer with delivery of a Medium body. The pour is with Minimal carbonation. Darkest brown, slight amber hue, frothy tan head slowly settles and lasts. A not surprise, Soft carbonation, medium body, low hopped.  A Mighty Awesomedesert beer a pleasant smells of cocoa and a very smooth.
Once introduced to Wooden Nickle Scottish Ale. I was then introduced to this  fine Gem. Much Stronger but, a true delight....The Quest!!! Onto the Quest!!! For Scottish Ale...WoW!!!
beer_name: Schlafly 21st Anniversary Single Malt Scottish Ale

review_blob: My Friends, It can clearly be said that I am the last and the least to say anything about beer. there are far better who can quantify. I have always taken a back seat . However, my friends I was introduced to a Mighty fine brew and the name "Wooden Nickel"  from Backpocket Brewing. I will never be the same. My Quest!!! In the Scottish Ale. Wow!!!
